text: Jack Peter Benedict Whitehall (born 7 July 1988) is an English comedian, actor, presenter and writer. He is known for starring as JP in the series Fresh Meat (2011–2016) and Alfie Wickers in the series* Cilford The Big Red Dog (2021) Bad Education (2012–2014, 2022–present) and its spin-off movie The Bad Education Movie (2015). ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:English television presenters Category:English television writers Category:Television personalities from London Category:Comedians from London Category:Actors from London Category:Writers from London
